  10 Jul 2002; Maik Schreiber <blizzy@gentoo.org> jdom-1.0_beta8-r1.ebuild files/digest-jdom-1.0_beta8-r1 :

  Added missing dependency on dev-java/ant. Thanks to
  Chris Winters for spotting this.

*jdom-1.0_beta8 (08 Jul 2002)

  08 Jul 2002; Maik Schreiber <blizzy@gentoo.org> :

